# Kernel Principal Component Analysis
# reference : http://scikit-learn.org/stable/modules/decomposition.html#decompositions

import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
from sklearn.decomposition import PCA, KernelPCA

# 입력 데이터 python pd 형식
inputArr = np.array(inputs[0])

# 입력 변수 처리
np.random.seed(0)
X = inputArr[:,9:14]

# kernel PCA 수행
## kernel : "linear" | "poly" | "rbf" | "sigmoid" | "cosine" | "precomputed"
kpca = KernelPCA(kernel="rbf", fit_inverse_transform=True, gamma=10)
X_kpca = kpca.fit_transform(X)
X_back = kpca.inverse_transform(X_kpca)
pca = PCA()
X_pca = pca.fit_transform(X)

# output 출력
pd_df = pd.DataFrame(X_pca, columns=['p_1','p_2','p_3','p_4','p_5'])
